<D>__{uh uh.}
<A>__{laz starts putting the cream on her scabbed knees. he rubs them gently.}
<C>__{lazarus}
<D>__{the seed that land on good soil is for them who hear the word of god... and understand the word of god. not enough for you to hear what i'm sayin', you gotta understand.}
