<D>__{look it. i've seen it in nature, i've seen it in men. ya got to change up your crop. cuz that seed ain't gettin' in.}
<P>__{(rae remains silent)}
<D>__{ya gotta cut this shit out. got no cause to be up under these fools, ruttin' on ya like you a bitch. like you somebody's dog. no woman... who joins in union with almighty god... or man... in the sanctity of marriage... should degrade herself... and bend to another man's will!}
